Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:47.62,Title,,0,0,240,,{\fad(800,800)}Gear Fourth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Corram! Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:18.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Corram para o centro da ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,O-Os edifícios que não foram cortados...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,...estão sendo arrastrados \Npara nós pela gaiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.52,Main,,0,0,0,,O país está ficando cada vez menor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:01.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,545)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(485,0)}PLANALTO REAL - NÍVEL 2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,A gaiola está encolhendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Então é por isso que há tanto alvoroço.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse é o verdadeiro terror da gaiola.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Que terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é muito sério!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Oh, eu chamei ele de querido de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso ficar de braços \Ncruzados esperando pela minha morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Acordem os que foram derrotados!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:37.94,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fs40\pos(1100,455)}PLANALTO REAL\N ANTIGO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Se a batalha continuar, até mesmo \Neste planalto será destruído.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:41.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu pensei que era o centro do país!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:43.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é o lugar mais seguro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhe para o céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.74,Main,,0,0,0,,O centro da gaiola está se movendo aos poucos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.16,Main,,0,0,0,,O centro da contração provavelmente é...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,...onde está Doflamingo, o atual planalto do rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:04:01.47,OPLetrerosInv,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,652)\fad(400,0)}LOCALIZAÇÃO ATUAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:01.47,OPLetrerosInv,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878,402)\fad(400,0)}PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:01.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Se for esse o caso, logo aqui também...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido, Hack! Rápido, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Rápido, por favor! Rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:09.56,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Pare de me sacudir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que descemos, \Nsem dúvida está um caos total.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Por ali, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoro-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Para onde diabos você está indo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:28.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é óbvio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.37,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Para detê-la, é claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquela coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Aquela coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.92,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Aquela coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.30,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fs40\pos(155,85)}FORA \NDO PALÁCIO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.30,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fs40\pos(155,490)}CAMPO\N DE GIRASSÓIS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Que surpresa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Não sabia que havia anões em Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Espero que seu braço volte ao normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que ele se recupera assim que \No sangue começa a circular.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sei, sou médico.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando vi o porto comercial subterrâneo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,eu percebi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,...que essa batalha,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.24,Main,,0,0,0,,mesmo que derrotemos Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,não vai terminar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Vai causar tremendas repercussões no mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,E vocês estarão no olho do furacão.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,É isso que pretendemos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Gear Fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Kinniku Fuusen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...Fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Bound Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:12.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, que tipo de piada é essa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Você ficou bem grande...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Achei que você teria algum plano secreto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Você nem consegue ficar de pé direito porque, por causa da borracha, fica só quicando.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Como você vai me derrotar desse jeito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Durante dois anos,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1938)}eu lutei contra animais enormes\N que pareciam monstros!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Para poder derrotá-los,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:53.80,Main,,0,0,0,,eu precisava desse corpo \Nenorme e dessa elasticidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.14,Main,,0,0,0,,De que adianta ser elástico?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...vai conseguir fazer nada contra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,...Kong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.28,Main,,0,0,0,,...Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,É o Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.24,Main,,0,0,0,,O que ele está fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Saiam da frente! Saiam da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você está aqui, Doflamingo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,É o que eu quero saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujam! Ele vai nos matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Não há escapatória!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Lá fora está a gaiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou no centro, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele realmente me mandou voar longe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está usando sua elasticidade para voar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.84,Main,,0,0,0,,...Rhino Schneider!{ゴムゴムの犀榴弾砲（リノシュナイダー） Gomu Gomu no Rino Shunaidā?, literalmente significando "Canhão de Borracha de Rinoceronte". O mesmo que eu disse antes}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Apareceu mais alguém!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,É enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele mandou Doflamingo voar com um chute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.91,Main,,0,0,0,,O que há com esse cara que parece uma bola?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ao endurecer sua pele com o Busoshoku Haki,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:01.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,ele aumenta muito sua tensão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa maldita bola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.88,Main,,0,0,0,,É só borracha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu já te disse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não é páreo para o meu Gear Fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...Culverin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Athlete!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:13.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ele está usando o Busoshoku Haki, mas ainda está usando as propriedades da borracha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse ataque...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,...não vai funcionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acredito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não vai escapar, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou acabar com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:30.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Agora ele só fica se alongando!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Continue perseguindo, Python!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Que insistente!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Caia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,...Culverin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,A bola de borracha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,...está esmagando...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...o Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem é esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Não importa quem seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:16.52,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,545)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(485,0)}PLANALTO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você viu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas que transformação.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.56,Main,,0,0,0,,É realmente o Chapéu de Palha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está esmagando o Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Que força incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ele está usando muito Haki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:34.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Usando muito Haki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, ali, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele foi para outro lugar lutar, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,E eu que me dei ao trabalho de vir aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:52.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,O Comandante da Primeira Divisão dos Piratas do Barba Negra, Jesus Burgess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Por que ele está aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Persegui-los ou esperar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Seja como for, não vou deixá-los escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou garantir que eu consiga o que quero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Como eu pensei, ele está atrás de Luffy-kun e sua tripulação.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:10.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Qual é o objetivo dele?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:16.79,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,545)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(789,0)}COLISEU CORRIDA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:16.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Viola...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:20.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Só resta a luta entre Luffy-kun e aquele cara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, é isso, pai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Dos oficiais ou superiores,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.98,Main,,0,0,0,,o único que ainda está de pé é Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:31.54,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,545)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(485,0)}FÁBRICA DE SMILE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Saiam da fábrica, Tontattas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.12,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Se apressem e saiam daí!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:49.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Já resgatamos os companheiros que ficaram para trás na fábrica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,A fábrica está inclinando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Fraland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que a fábrica de Smile é\N a única que não foi cortada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Só a fábrica?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim, por causa do kairouseki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Kairouseki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:17.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, as paredes externas da \Nfábrica são feitas de kairouseki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso, os fios criados por um usuário de Akuma no Mi não conseguem cortá-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele começou a empurrá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã? Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Robô-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoroland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Moñoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.33,Main,,0,0,0,,O centro do país está na \Ndireção de onde vocês vieram voando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Se quiserem fugir, vão para o outro lado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Não estamos fugindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Viemos para deter os fios!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Deter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, nem pensei nisso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.32,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.04,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:10.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Enquanto Luffy dá um fim nisso, \Nnós vamos ganhar tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Já sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:20.24,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,485)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(794,0)}CENTRO DA CIDADE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:20.24,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,710)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(794,0)}LUFFY CONTRA DOFLAMINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:39.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ele está usando o Busoshoku Haki para controlar a expansão e contração da borracha à vontade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:47.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ele combinou o Busoshoku Haki com a borracha, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu demorar muito, o Gear Fourth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que você dominou\N bem suas habilidades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas deve ser uma carga pesada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Deve haver riscos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha, quantos \Nsegundos você ainda aguenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.01,Main,,0,0,0,,...Double...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:25.08,Main,,0,0,0,,No entanto, meus fios não se esgotam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...Culverin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Off White!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:34.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que há fios saindo do chão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você fez com esta cidade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Escuta, garoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,As habilidades das Akumas no Mi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:51.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...têm um estágio superior chamado "despertar"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Os prédios se transformaram em fios!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Em casos raros, uma habilidade "despertará" e começará a afetar outras coisas além do corpo do usuário!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Várias coisas estão se transformando em fios!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Não parece ser Paramecia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo ao seu redor está se transformando em fios!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Você nem consegue se aproximar de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:40.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando sua força acabar, meu corpo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando seu Haki acabar,\N eu darei o golpe final!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:18.80,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1125,435)}{\pos(638,710)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(300,300)}20 MINUTOS\N DEPOIS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele vai nos cortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, vovó!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:34.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Vovó, levante-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Os fios vão te cortar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.37,Main,,0,0,0,,É impossível...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Não consigo mais correr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe aqui e siga em frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Não! Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, não vou sobreviver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, levante-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:03.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que eu me levante, não conseguirei\N correr até o centro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém nos ajude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ainda há pacientes no hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Não podemos carregar todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Não encontro meu filho!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém o viu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está usando uma camiseta do Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele tem cinco anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém viu meu filho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, todos vamos morrer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos desistir...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:43.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que fujamos e fujamos, \Ncontinuaremos dentro da jaula!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo vai acabar nos matando.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.86,Main,,0,0,0,,É mais fácil...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,...desistir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Escutem todos, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.95,0:22:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,...o antigo rei de Dressrosa, Riku Dold III.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,R-Rei Riku...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Por causa do jogo que Doflamingo começou, este país está...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,...dentro de uma enorme gaiola \Nda qual não se pode escapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso, essa gaiola brutal continua \Nencolhendo e cortando a cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Riku...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles descobriram a verdade de repente...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Com certeza, eles ainda não sabem o que pensar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:05.78,Main,,0,0,0,,...e estão apenas lutando para \Nproteger suas próprias vidas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:11.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas isso não é um sonho!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,E nenhuma tragédia aconteceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Durante dez anos, nós...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.68,0:23:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,...estivemos dentro de \Numa gaiola governada por piratas...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,...chamada Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}Durante dez anos, fomos marionetes, \Nvivendo como eles queriam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:41.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa é a realidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas tudo isso vai acabar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:45.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,A Família Donquixote, que pensávamos \Nque ninguém poderia derrotar,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,quase foi completamente aniquilada \Npelas mãos de fortes guerreiros...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.15,0:23:57.47,Main,,0,0,0,,...que por acaso estavam no país!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles já derrotaram todos \Nos oficiais da família!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:01.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Aqueles oficiais...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Foram derrotados?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.29,0:24:08.43,Main,,0,0,0,,O único inimigo que resta para derrotar...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:12.76,Main,,0,0,0,,...é Doflamingo, o atual rei de Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:28.78,Main,,0,0,0,,E quem está lutando contra ele \Né o pirata Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.78,0:24:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele certamente será capaz \Nde destruir a gaiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Seja ele vitorioso ou não, \Nfaltam apenas alguns minutos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.29,0:24:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Até lá, fujam em segurança, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Não deixem que ninguém seja esmagado \Npor este país que está encolhendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.43,0:24:51.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Continuem correndo, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.88,0:24:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que não aguentem mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.00,0:24:56.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que quebrem as pernas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:25:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Sobrevivam por mais alguns \Nminutos, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.65,0:25:10.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Há esperança!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.08,0:25:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Não desistam, por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.68,0:25:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer isso sozinhos, se for preciso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.65,0:25:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.65,0:25:24.25,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:25.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos correr, neta!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.30,0:25:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Vovó!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.59,0:25:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.18,0:25:40.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Como o Rei Riku disse,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.40,0:25:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,vamos correr para o centro \Nsem desistir!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.18,0:25:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Carreguem os doentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.95,0:25:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Transportem as camas!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Mãe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.20,0:26:06.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Sobrevivam até o final!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Até que Chapéu de Palha Luffy nos faça o favor de derrotar Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.78,0:26:12.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.80,0:26:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:27.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Morra de uma vez por todas!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.01,0:26:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho mais tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.61,0:26:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Toda a cidade está se transformando em fios!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.55,0:26:36.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Billow White!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.96,0:26:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.37,0:26:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Voe para longe!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.86,0:27:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.53,0:27:26.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Este é o golpe final!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.06,0:27:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.46,0:27:41.22,Main,,0,0,0,,...Leo Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.68,0:28:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.38,0:28:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
